ActJudges Act (Removal Allowance) Order
SubjectJeffrey J. Oliphant Removal Allowance Order RELOCATION EXPENSES
PrecisOrder prescribing an additional period from December 15, 2009 to December 14, 2010, during which the difference between the sale price of the former residence and its fair market value may be reimbursed to the Hon. JEFFREY J. OLIPHANT, who was required to relocate to the City of Brandon, Manitoba, following his reassignment.
